Package com.bcs2024.knapsack.algorithm.dancinglinks

Class ParcelInfo

java.lang.Object
com.bcs2024.knapsack.algorithm.dancinglinks.ParcelInfo
public class ParcelInfo extends Object
Represents detailed information about a parcel in the context of the knapsack problem. It includes the parcel's identifier, position, shape, and value.

  • Constructor Details

    • ParcelInfo

      public ParcelInfo(int id, int x, int y, int z0, int parcelID, int[][][] shape, int pieceValue)
      Constructs a ParcelInfo object with specified parameters, representing a parcel's details.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique identifier for this instance of parcel information.
      x - The x-coordinate of the parcel's position in the cargo space.
      y - The y-coordinate of the parcel's position in the cargo space.
      z0 - The z-coordinate of the parcel's position in the cargo space.
      parcelID - The identifier of the parcel type.
      shape - The 3D array representing the shape of the parcel.
      pieceValue - The value of the parcel.
